164
00:17:35,753 --> 00:17:36,795
- Virkelig?
- Ja.

165
00:17:36,962 --> 00:17:39,715
De er fantastiske.
De er smukke.

166
00:17:39,882 --> 00:17:42,259
- Tak.
- Hvor har du lært at male?

167
00:17:42,426 --> 00:17:45,638
